      "message": "at proto level, there is no such thing as \"content is nil\".\nit can be empty, but it can\u0027t be nil.\n\nas you said, empty artifact is a valid case, so I think content_hash presence should not depend on whether content is empty.\n\n(but then again, I don\u0027t think content_hash field is needed here to begin with. There is another thread about this)",
